ner_t"></ul>                                               </div>                                    <div id="pic_move"><div class="pic_move_left"><img src="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/yzyd/Templates/YuZhouYaoDu/Images/pic_show_left_yuzhou.png" /></div><div class="pic_move_right"><img src="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/yzyd/Templates/YuZhouYaoDu/Images/pic_show_right_yuzhou.png" /></div></div>                                    </div>                            </div>                           </div>                    <!--遗迹访谈-->                     <div class="Content_Video">                            <div class="Content_Video_title">                            <a href="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/yzyd/YiJiFangTan/Video/20144/VideoContent_5.html">遗迹访谈</a>                            </div>                             <div class="Video_show_scroll">                                    <div class="pic_little">                                        <div class="Video_scroll">                                            <ul id="container_02">                                                <li><a href="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/yzyd/YiJiFangTan/Video/20144/VideoContent_5.html"><img src="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/fileapi/image/2014/7/8/130492965572009639_0.jpeg" /></a><a href="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/yzyd/YiJiFangTan/Video/20144/VideoContent_5.html"><span>怀帮会馆考察</span></a></li> <li><a href="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/yzyd/YiJiFangTan/Video/20144/VideoContent_4.html"><img src="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/fileapi/image/2014/7/8/130492966106720223_0.jpeg" /></a><a href="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/yzyd/YiJiFangTan/Video/20144/VideoContent_4.html"><span>老药工讲花蕊</span></a></li> <li><a href="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/yzyd/YiJiFangTan/Video/20144/VideoContent_3.html"><img src="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/fileapi/image/2014/7/8/130492966921466824_0.jpeg" /></a><a href="https://tcmchina.hactcm.edu.cn/yzyd/YiJiFangTan/Video/20144/VideoConten